OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering 'good
OL,4,CSamaritan' in Sheffield
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for life in
OL,7,Fprison with a minimum term of 26 years
OL,8,Ffor the murder of father-of-two Chris
OL,9,FMarriott, who stopped to help a woman
OL,10,Flying in the road after a wedding day
OL,11,Fbrawl in Sheffield.
OL,13,FTwenty-five-year-old Hassan Jhangur
OL,14,Farrived at the scene of the feuding
OL,15,Ffamilies in his Seat Ibiza, first
OL,16,Fdriving into the father of the other
OL,17,Ffamily Riasat Khan before ploughing
OL,18,Finto a crowd of people, including
OL,19,FChris Marriott, who died from his
OL,20,Finjuries.
