OL,6,FJhangur, of Whiteways Road, Sheffield,
OL,7,Fthen got out of the car and stabbed
OL,8,Fhis new brother-in-law, Hasan Khan,
OL,9,Fseveral times in the left ear and
OL,10,Fback. Hasan Khan had married his
OL,11,Fsister Amaani hours earlier.
OL,13,FCharity worker Mr Marriott was out for
OL,14,Fa post-Christmas walk with his family
OL,15,Fon 27 December 2023 when he came
OL,16,Facross the commotion and stopped to
OL,17,Fhelp Hassan Jhangur's sister Nafeesa
OL,18,Flying in the road on College Close,
OL,19,FBurngreave.
