OL,6,FA group of four including Mr Marriott,
OL,7,FJhangur's sister Nafeesa, his mother
OL,8,FAmbreen Jhangur and midwife Alison
OL,9,FNorris were all assisting Nafeesa and
OL,10,Fwere struck by Hassan Jhangur's car.
OL,12,FPolice described Mr Marriott as a
OL,13,F"good Samaritan" who had paid for his
OL,14,Fkindness with his life.
OL,16,FToday his grieving widow Bryony
OL,17,FMarriott spoke at Sheffield Crown
OL,18,FCourt and said he was someone with a
OL,19,Fcompassionate heart who loved helping
OL,20,Fothers.
