OL,6,FShe said: "Chris was genuine, kind,
OL,7,Fand loving. There's no area in our
OL,8,Flives that hasn't been affected by
OL,9,FChris' death."
OL,11,FThe Court also heard a statement from
OL,12,FMs Norris, who suffered a leg injury
OL,13,Fin the incident. She says she is still
OL,14,Fbeing treated for PTSD with her family
OL,15,Fwho have witnessed the incident have
OL,16,Fexperienced anxiety.
