OL,6,FIn his sentencing of Hassan Jhangur,
OL,7,Fjudge Honourable Mr Justice Morris
OL,8,Fsaid "It is clear that Chris was a
OL,9,Fmuch loved husband, father and son and
OL,10,Fa highly respected member of the wider
OL,11,Flocal community.
OL,13,F"This was a deliberate and senseless
OL,14,Fact of hot-headed and wanton violence
OL,15,Fresulting in the tragic death of Chris
OL,16,FMarriott and life-changing
OL,17,Fconsequences for many others."
