OL,6,FJhangur's father, 57-year-old Mohammed
OL,7,FJhangur of Whiteways Road, Sheffield,
OL,8,Fwas found guilty of perverting the
OL,9,Fcourse of justice after he concealed a
OL,10,Fknife.
OL,12,FIn the commotion following the
OL,13,Fincidents on College Close, Mohammed
OL,14,FJhangur was heard saying to his son,
OL,15,F"Give me the knife before anyone
OL,16,Fnotices it."
OL,18,FPolice found the knife in the boot of
OL,19,FMohammed Jhangur's taxi. He has been
OL,20,Fgiven a six month sentence suspended
OL,21,Ffor two years.
